round

changing your form your physical state
what is alive within you is unaffected
by what you know of as dying

Earth

hypnotized rabbit in front of a snake
won't you move you threaten to be
swallowed up by events and don't realize
it
why is it the way it is
most who hear this may become shall I
say irked by such words
but I know a small handful will move
deeper into spiritual action
it is you that I am speaking to now
it is time to perhaps stop beating
around the bush like a cat circling
around your unresolved life issues
face them head on now my beloved
Brethren of Light have no fear call upon
the Creator the father mother of your

place the Creator forth before your
every trouble and then surrender
watch what will happen when you do this
my great friends
the only important thing now is to live

Infinity of it
foreign

development or non-development in the

vantage point

in

freedom for yourself and for those
around you even if they are your
children
one day you will have to let them go and
they will go their own way
all life regulates itself through the
Creator and in the end the natural

the human mind clouded by the ego can
often make this natural conclusion a
long way around but it does not have to

ask your higher self for all your
lessons to be brought to you with ease
and with Grace henceforth
in heaven as on Earth growth occurs out

beings

space-time concept of the earth it is
important to wait for this moment of
Awakening
